criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Women who choose to terminate pregnancy because of maternal factors in the First
             Affiliated Hospital of Sun Yat-sen University at the 6-10 weeks of gestation.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Younger than 18 years old;

          -  Older than 40 years old;

          -  Diagnosed DM before pregnancy;

          -  Complicated with other diseases such as GDM, insulin resistance, obesity and related
             endocrine diseases, etc.;
